                                        <H2 STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: justify;">Your Practice &amp; Business</H2>
                                        <P STYLE="line-height: 14pt;">This website is full of marketing ideas specifically for independent healthcare and fitness practitioners. Whether you are a solo practitioner, a group practice manager or a marketing manager, there are ideas on this site for you. This website will also show you how to put the ideas into practice. Regular, location-specific marketing in an efficient, ethical manner is important in order to keep the pool of clients refreshed. For more on this<SPAN STYLE="color: rgb(0,0,154);"> <A HREF="./html/tools.html">click here</A>.</SPAN></P>
                                        <H2 STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: justify;">Sloan Consultants㰥ciality</H2>
                                        <P STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: justify;">We are experts and specialists in building up the business and client base of all kinds of healthcare and fitness practitioners. Sloan Hickman, the founding partner, spent five years at Primal Pictures Ltd., the 3D anatomy developer and publisher, building cash-flow for the company and income streams for independent practitioners who lectured as part of their professional life. Prior experience was 15 years in advertising in both the USA and London. This background is fleshed out by a network of collaborators with expertise in SMEs, direct mail production and targeting; on-line marketing; public speaking; graphic and web design; and television and radio production</P>
                                        <H3 STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: left;"><A HREF="./html/results.html#Testimonial"><SPAN STYLE="color: rgb(0,0,154);"><U>CLICK here to read what others say</U>!</SPAN></A><BR>&nbsp;</H3>
                                        <H2 STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: justify;">More benefits:</H2>
                                        <H3 STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: justify;">Creating Preference</H3>
                                        <P STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: justify;">Utilising some or all of the ideas in these pages will help you bring more clients to your practice.</P>
                                        <H3>Widening your Referral base</H3>
                                        <P STYLE="font-family: Verdana,Tahoma,Arial,Helvetica,Sans-serif,sans-serif; font-size: xx-small; line-height: 14pt; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; text-align: left;">There are ways to meet more doctors and alternative specialists without buying lunch for the entire office! <A HREF="./html/tools.html"><SPAN STYLE="color: rgb(0,0,154);">More here</SPAN>.</A></P>
                                        <H3>Raising local awareness</H3>
                                        <P STYLE="line-height: 14pt; text-align: left;">Raise the awareness and knowledge of your services in your community. This is very location specific and somewhat labour intensive, but the rewards are great.</P>
                                        <H5 STYLE="text-align: left;"><SPAN STYLE="font-size: xx-small;">Education can solve the problems to do with public health. To this end we want to publicise the skills of, and raise the awareness of the public to, the local existence of health and fitness practitioners world-wide. </SPAN></TD>
